title: Yin Yoga
description: Join Lazuli Moon for a calming yin yoga class. This class is perfect for beginners and anyone looking to relax and release tension.

title: Hatha Yoga
description: Join Indigo Sky for a gentle hatha yoga class. This class is perfect for all levels and focuses on the basics of yoga poses and breathwork.

title: Vinyasa Yoga
description: Join Aurora Borealis for a dynamic vinyasa yoga class. This class is perfect for intermediate and advanced students and focuses on flowing sequences of poses with breath.

title: Yogalates
description: Join Phoenix Rising for a fusion class of yoga and pilates. This class is perfect for all levels and focuses on strengthening and toning the body.

title: Ashtanga Yoga
description: Join Saffron Sage for a dynamic and challenging Ashtanga yoga class. This class is perfect for advanced students and focuses on a set series of poses with breath and movement.
